            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.158,
                0.199,
                0.185
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\frac{3}{2}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.195,
                0.813,
                0.239
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{(1 + \\cos x)\\ln(1 + x)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{\\ln(1 + x)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.358,
                0.248,
                0.652,
                0.276
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\frac {1}{2} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(3 \\frac {\\sin x}{x} + x \\cos \\frac {1}{x}\\right) = \\frac {3}{2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.283,
                0.236,
                0.298
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\((-2,4)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.306,
                0.722,
                0.338
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为幂级数 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}na_n(x - 1)^{n + 1}\\) 的收敛半径与 \\(\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}a_{n}x^{n}\\) 的收敛半径相同，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.344,
                0.83,
                0.375
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所以 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}na_n(x - 1)^{n + 1}\\) 的收敛半径为 \\(R = 3\\) ，故所求收敛区间为 \\(-3 < x - 1 < 3\\) ，即 \\((-2,4)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.381,
                0.289,
                0.404
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\( y = -x + \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}} \\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.41,
                0.457,
                0.447
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 对数螺线的参数方程为 \\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l}x = \\mathrm{e}^{\\theta}\\cos \\theta ,\\\\ y = \\mathrm{e}^{\\theta}\\sin \\theta . \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.455,
                0.363,
                0.482
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{2}\\) 时，\\((x, y) = (0, \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}})\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.49,
                0.512,
                0.524
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{dy} / \\mathrm{d}\\theta}{\\mathrm{dx} / \\mathrm{d}\\theta} = \\frac{\\cos\\theta + \\sin\\theta}{\\cos\\theta - \\sin\\theta},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right|_{\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{2}} = -1,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.53,
                0.611,
                0.552
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故所求切线的直角坐标方程为 \\(y - \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}} = -x\\) ，或 \\(y = -x + \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.559,
                0.202,
                0.572
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 -3."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.579,
                0.687,
                0.594
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】方法一 因为 \\(B \\neq O\\) 且 \\(AB = O\\) ，所以方程组 \\(AX = 0\\) 有非零解，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.601,
                0.66,
                0.658
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(|\\mathbf{A}| = 0\\) ，而由 \\(|\\mathbf{A}| = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc}1 & 2 & -2\\\\ 4 & t & 3\\\\ 3 & -1 & 1 \\end{array} \\right| = 7t + 21 = 0\\) ，得 \\(t = -3\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.664,
                0.444,
                0.679
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二 由 \\(\\mathbf{AB} = \\mathbf{O}\\) 得 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) + r(\\mathbf{B})\\leqslant 3\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.685,
                0.682,
                0.7
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由 \\(\\pmb{B} \\neq \\pmb{0}\\) 得 \\(r(\\pmb{B}) \\geqslant 1\\) ，于是 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) \\leqslant 2 < 3\\) ，故 \\(|\\mathbf{A}| = 0\\) ，解得 \\(t = -3\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.708,
                0.197,
                0.734
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(5)【答案】 \\(\\frac{2}{5}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.743,
                0.796,
                0.758
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】令 \\(A_{1} = \\{\\) 第一个人取黄球 \\(\\}\\), \\(A_{2} = \\{\\) 第一个人取白球 \\(\\}\\), \\(B = \\{\\) 第二个人取黄球 \\(\\}\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.218,
                0.767,
                0.801,
                0.793
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nP \\left(A _ {1}\\right) = \\frac {2}{5}, \\quad P \\left(A _ {2}\\right) = \\frac {3}{5}, \\quad P \\left(B \\mid A _ {1}\\right) = \\frac {1 9}{4 9}, \\quad P \\left(B \\mid A _ {2}\\right) = \\frac {2 0}{4 9},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.801,
                0.503,
                0.815
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(P(B) = P(A_{1})P(B\\mid A_{1}) + P(A_{2})P(B\\mid A_{2})\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.167,
                0.824,
                0.4,
                0.85
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\frac {2}{5} \\times \\frac {1 9}{4 9} + \\frac {3}{5} \\times \\frac {2 0}{4 9} = \\frac {2}{5}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.858,
                0.141,
                0.873
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.879,
                0.199,
                0.894
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（1）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.902,
                0.799,
                0.937
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(\\lim_{\\substack{x\\to 0\\\\ y = x}}f(x,y) = \\frac{1}{2}\\neq \\lim_{\\substack{x\\to 0\\\\ y = -x}}f(x,y) = -\\frac{1}{2}\\)，所以 \\(f(x,y)\\) 在(0，0）处不连续；"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.074,
                0.71,
                0.102
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x,0) - f(0,0)}{x - 0} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{0}{x} = 0\\) 得 \\(f_{x}^{\\prime}(0,0) = 0\\) ，同理 \\(f_{y}^{\\prime}(0,0) = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.111,
                0.421,
                0.126
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\(f(x,y)\\) 在 \\((0,0)\\) 处可偏导，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.134,
                0.212,
                0.149
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.156,
                0.472,
                0.172
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\( f^{\\prime}(x) < 0 \\) 得 \\( f(x) \\) 为单调减函数，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.178,
                0.565,
                0.206
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(S_{1} = \\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x > \\int_{a}^{b}f(b)\\mathrm{d}x = f(b)(b - a) = S_{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.213,
                0.393,
                0.229
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由 \\(f''(x) > 0\\) 得 \\(f(x)\\) 为凹函数，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.237,
                0.791,
                0.265
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(S_{1} = \\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x <   \\frac{1}{2} [f(a) + f(b)](b - a) = S_{3}\\) ，即 \\(S_{2} <   S_{1} <   S_{3}\\) ，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.275,
                0.214,
                0.29
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 （A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.297,
                0.425,
                0.312
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 由周期函数定积分的平移性质得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.206,
                0.319,
                0.676,
                0.382
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} F (x) = \\int_ {- \\pi} ^ {\\pi} \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} \\sin t \\mathrm {d} t = \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} [ \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} \\sin t + \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin (- t)} \\sin (- t) ] \\mathrm {d} t \\\\ = \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\left(\\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} - \\mathrm {e} ^ {- \\sin t}\\right) \\sin t \\mathrm {d} t, \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.39,
                0.552,
                0.406
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(t \\in [0, \\pi]\\) 时，\\((\\mathrm{e}^{\\sin t} - \\mathrm{e}^{-\\sin t})\\sin t \\geqslant 0\\)，则 \\(F(x) > 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.414,
                0.336,
                0.429
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(F(x)\\) 为正常数，应选（A）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.437,
                0.214,
                0.451
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(4)【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.459,
                0.772,
                0.521
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】三条直线交于一点的充分必要条件是方程组 \\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} a_{1}x + b_{1}y = -c_{1}, \\\\ a_{2}x + b_{2}y = -c_{2}, \\\\ a_{3}x + b_{3}y = -c_{3} \\end{array} \\right.\\) 有唯一解，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.529,
                0.643,
                0.591
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) = r(\\overline{\\mathbf{A}}) = 2\\) ，其中 \\(\\mathbf{A} = \\begin{pmatrix} a_1 & b_1 \\\\ a_2 & b_2 \\\\ a_3 & b_3 \\end{pmatrix}, \\overline{\\mathbf{A}} = \\begin{pmatrix} a_1 & b_1 & -c_1 \\\\ a_2 & b_2 & -c_2 \\\\ a_3 & b_3 & -c_3 \\end{pmatrix}\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.599,
                0.534,
                0.615
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\alpha_{3}\\) 线性相关，而 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2}\\) 线性无关，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.622,
                0.214,
                0.636
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.644,
                0.414,
                0.659
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 已知 \\(D(X) = 4\\) ， \\(D(Y) = 2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.666,
                0.791,
                0.704
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(X, Y\\) 相互独立，所以 \\(D(3X - 2Y) = 9D(X) + 4D(Y) = 36 + 8 = 44\\) ，应选(D).三、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.712,
                0.718,
                0.748
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 平面曲线 \\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} y^{2} = 2z, \\\\ x = 0 \\end{array} \\right.\\) 绕 \\(z\\) 轴旋转一周形成的曲面为 \\(\\Sigma: x^{2} + y^{2} = 2z\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.755,
                0.793,
                0.772
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\Omega = \\{(x,y,z) \\mid (x,y) \\in D_z, 0 \\leqslant z \\leqslant 8\\}\\)，其中 \\(D_z = \\{(x,y) \\mid x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 2z\\}\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.779,
                0.67,
                0.817
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(I = \\iiint_{\\Omega}(x^{2} + y^{2})\\mathrm{d}v = \\int_{0}^{8}\\mathrm{d}z\\iint_{D_{z}}(x^{2} + y^{2})\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = 2\\pi \\int_{0}^{8}\\mathrm{d}z\\int_{0}^{\\sqrt{2z}}r^{3}\\mathrm{d}r\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.156,
                0.822,
                0.348,
                0.85
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {8} z ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} z = \\frac {1 0 2 4 \\pi}{3}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.859,
                0.22,
                0.874
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（2）【解】 方法一"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.882,
                0.57,
                0.941
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(C:\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}x = \\cos t,\\\\ y = \\sin t,\\\\ z = 2 - \\cos t + \\sin t \\end{array} \\right.\\) （起点 \\(t = 2\\pi\\) ，终点 \\(t = 0\\) )，则"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.073,
                0.816,
                0.243
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {C} (z - y) \\mathrm {d} x + (x - z) \\mathrm {d} y + (x - y) \\mathrm {d} z \\\\ = \\int_ {2 \\pi} ^ {0} (2 - \\cos t) (- \\sin t) d t + (2 \\cos t - 2 - \\sin t) \\cos t d t + (\\cos t - \\sin t) (\\sin t + \\cos t) d t \\\\ = \\int_ {2 \\pi} ^ {0} (3 \\cos^ {2} t - \\sin^ {2} t - 2 \\sin t - 2 \\cos t) d t \\\\ = - 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\cos^ {2} t d t + \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\sin^ {2} t d t = - 1 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\cos^ {2} t d t + 4 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\sin^ {2} t d t \\\\ = - 8 \\times \\frac {1}{2} \\times \\frac {\\pi}{2} = - 2 \\pi . \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.252,
                0.14,
                0.267
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.273,
                0.405,
                0.289
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "设 \\(C\\) 所在的截口平面块为 \\(\\Sigma\\) ，方向向下，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.077,
                0.296,
                0.722,
                0.328
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "取 \\(n = \\{-1, 1, -1\\}\\), 方向余弦为 \\(\\cos \\alpha = -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}, \\cos \\beta = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}, \\cos \\gamma = -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}\\), 则"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.336,
                0.8,
                0.497
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {C} (z - y) \\mathrm {d} x + (x - z) \\mathrm {d} y + (x - y) \\mathrm {d} z = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\left| \\begin{array}{c c c} - 1 & 1 & - 1 \\\\ \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial x} & \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial y} & \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial z} \\\\ z - y & x - z & x - y \\end{array} \\right| \\mathrm {d} S = - \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\mathrm {d} S \\\\ = - \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} \\sqrt {1 + \\left(\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x}\\right) ^ {2} + \\left(\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y}\\right) ^ {2}} d x d y \\\\ = - 2 \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} d x d y = - 2 \\pi . \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.047,
                0.5,
                0.218,
                0.515
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【解】 由题意得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.416,
                0.523,
                0.586,
                0.574
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} x}{\\mathrm {d} t} = k x (N - x), \\\\ x (0) = x _ {0}, \\end{array} \\right.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.582,
                0.452,
                0.61
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{d}x}{x(N - x)} = k\\mathrm{d}t\\) 得 \\(\\frac{1}{N}\\ln \\frac{x}{N - x} = kt + C,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.619,
                0.614,
                0.651
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(x(0) = x_0\\) 得 \\(C = \\frac{1}{N}\\ln \\frac{x_0}{N - x_0}\\)，故 \\(x(t) = \\frac{Nx_0\\mathrm{e}^{kNt}}{N - x_0 + x_0\\mathrm{e}^{kNt}}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.047,
                0.658,
                0.078,
                0.672
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、"
        },
