            "content": "(2)【解】 \\(\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = f^{\\prime}(\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y)\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y,\\quad \\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial y} = f^{\\prime}(\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y)\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cos y,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.907,
                0.51,
                0.936
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x ^ {2}} = f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (e ^ {x} \\sin y) (e ^ {x} \\sin y) ^ {2} + f ^ {\\prime} (e ^ {x} \\sin y) e ^ {x} \\sin y,\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.073,
                0.536,
                0.104
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial y ^ {2}} = f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\sin y\\right) \\left(\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\cos y\\right) ^ {2} - f ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\sin y\\right) \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\sin y,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.1,
                0.11,
                0.832,
                0.143
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\frac{\\partial^2z}{\\partial x^2} + \\frac{\\partial^2z}{\\partial y^2} = f''(\\mathrm{e}^x\\sin y)\\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\), 令 \\(\\mathrm{e}^x\\sin y = u\\), 由 \\(\\frac{\\partial^2z}{\\partial x^2} + \\frac{\\partial^2z}{\\partial y^2} = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}z\\) 得 \\(f''(u) - f(u) = 0\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.1,
                0.148,
                0.714,
                0.165
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(f^{\\prime \\prime}(u) - f(u) = 0\\) 的通解为 \\(f(u) = C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-u} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^u\\) （ \\(C_1,C_2\\) 为任意常数)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.068,
                0.173,
                0.512,
                0.198
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】 由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{x} = A\\) 得 \\(f(0) = 0,f^{\\prime}(0) = A\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.208,
                0.295,
                0.222
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x = 0\\) 时， \\(\\varphi (0) = 0\\)"
