        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.228,
                0.539,
                0.269
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x \\neq 0\\) 时，\\(\\varphi(x) = \\frac{1}{x} \\int_{0}^{1} f(xt) \\, \\mathrm{d}(xt) = \\frac{\\int_{0}^{x} f(u) \\, \\mathrm{d}u}{x}\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.279,
                0.378,
                0.34
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\(\\varphi (x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}0, & x = 0,\\\\ \\frac{\\int_0^xf(u)\\mathrm{d}u}{x}, & x\\neq 0. \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.349,
                0.448,
                0.39
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x\\neq 0\\) 时， \\(\\varphi^{\\prime}(x) = \\frac{xf(x) - \\int_{0}^{x}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u}{x^{2}};\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.401,
                0.792,
                0.442
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x = 0\\) 时，由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\varphi(x) - \\varphi(0)}{x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\int_0^xf(u)\\mathrm{d}u}{x^2} = \\frac{1}{2}\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{x} = \\frac{A}{2}\\) 得 \\(\\varphi^{\\prime}(0) = \\frac{A}{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.453,
                0.472,
                0.531
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(\\varphi^{\\prime}(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll} \\frac{A}{2}, & x = 0, \\\\ \\frac{xf(x) - \\int_{0}^{x}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u}{x^{2}}, & x \\neq 0. \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
