            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\varphi '(x) = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\left[\\frac{f(x)}{x} -\\frac{\\int_0^xf(u)\\mathrm{d}u}{x^2}\\right] = \\frac{A}{2} = \\varphi '(0)\\)，所以 \\(\\varphi^{\\prime}(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处连续"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.069,
                0.593,
                0.617,
                0.618
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "六、【证明】（1）由 \\(a_{n + 1} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left(a_n + \\frac{1}{a}\\right)\\geqslant 1\\) ，得数列 \\(\\{a_{n}\\}\\) 有下界；"
