            "content": "由 \\(a_{n + 1} - a_n = \\frac{1}{2}\\left(a_n + \\frac{1}{a_n}\\right) - a_n = \\frac{1 - a_n^2}{2a_n} \\leqslant 0\\) ，得数列 \\(\\{a_{n}\\}\\) 单调递减，"
