            "content": "级数 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}(a_n - a_{n+1})\\) 展开得 \\(S_n = (a_1 - a_2) + (a_2 - a_3) + \\dots + (a_n - a_{n+1}) = 2 - a_{n+1}\\),"
