            "content": "令 \\(\\pmb{\\beta}_{1} = \\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 2 \\\\ 3 \\end{pmatrix}\\)，\\(\\pmb{\\beta}_{2} = \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} - \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\beta}_{1})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{1}, \\pmb{\\beta}_{1})} \\pmb{\\beta}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} -1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 4 \\\\ -1 \\end{pmatrix} - \\frac{1}{3} \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 2 \\\\ 3 \\end{pmatrix} = \\frac{2}{3} \\begin{pmatrix} -2 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 5 \\\\ -3 \\end{pmatrix}\\)，"
