            "content": "则 \\(\\mathbf{B}\\mathbf{X} = \\mathbf{0}\\) 的解空间的一个标准正交基为 \\(\\gamma_{1} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{15}}\\left[ \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ 1\\\\ 2\\\\ 3 \\end{array} \\right],\\quad \\gamma_{2} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{39}}\\left[ \\begin{array}{l} - 2\\\\ 1\\\\ 5\\\\ -3 \\end{array} \\right].\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.237,
                0.642,
                0.294
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】（I）由 \\(\\left( \\begin{array}{rrr}2 & -1 & 2\\\\ 5 & a & 3\\\\ -1 & b & -2 \\end{array} \\right)\\left( \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ 1\\\\ -1 \\end{array} \\right) = \\lambda \\left( \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ 1\\\\ -1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) 得 \\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} - 1 = \\lambda ,\\\\ a + 2 = \\lambda ,\\\\ b + 1 = -\\lambda , \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
