            "content": "（Ⅱ） \\(\\left|\\lambda E - A\\right| = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc}\\lambda -2 & 1 & -2\\\\ -5 & \\lambda +3 & -3\\\\ 1 & 0 & \\lambda +2 \\end{array} \\right| = (\\lambda +1)^3 = 0\\) 得 \\(\\lambda_{1} = \\lambda_{2} = \\lambda_{3} = -1\\)"
