            "content": "\\[\n- \\boldsymbol {E} - \\boldsymbol {A} = \\left(\\begin{array}{c c c}- 3&1&- 2\\\\- 5&2&- 3\\\\1&0&1\\end{array}\\right)\\rightarrow \\left(\\begin{array}{c c c}1&0&1\\\\0&1&1\\\\0&0&0\\end{array}\\right),\n\\]"
