            "content": "九、【解】 显然 \\(X \\sim B\\left(3, \\frac{2}{5}\\right)\\)，即 \\(P\\{X = k\\} = \\mathrm{C}_3^k\\left(\\frac{2}{5}\\right)^k\\left(\\frac{3}{5}\\right)^{3 - k}, k = 0,1,2,3;\\)"
