            "content": "当 \\(0 \\leqslant x < 1\\) 时，\\(F(x) = P\\{X \\leqslant x\\} = P\\{X = 0\\} = \\frac{27}{125}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.667,
                0.695,
                0.693
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(1 \\leqslant x < 2\\) 时，\\(F(x) = P\\{X \\leqslant x\\} = P\\{X = 0\\} + P\\{X = 1\\} = \\frac{81}{125}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.702,
