            "content": "当 \\(2 \\leqslant x < 3\\) 时，\\(F(x) = P\\{X \\leqslant x\\} = P\\{X = 0\\} + P\\{X = 1\\} + P\\{X = 2\\} = \\frac{117}{125}\\)"
