            "content": "即 \\(F(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}0, & x <   0,\\\\ \\frac{27}{125}, & 0\\leqslant x <   1,\\\\ \\frac{81}{125}, & 1\\leqslant x <   2,\\\\ \\frac{117}{125}, & 2\\leqslant x <   3,\\\\ 1, & x\\geqslant 3. \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
