            "angle": 0,
            "content": "十、【解】 \\(E(X) = \\int_0^1 xf(x)\\mathrm{d}x = (\\theta +1)\\int_0^1 x^{\\theta +1}\\mathrm{d}x = \\frac{\\theta + 1}{\\theta + 2},\\)"
